---
// Reusable "work in progress" banner for pillar pages still being built.
// Drop <UnderConstruction /> near the top of a pillar's MDX. Pass child content
// to override the default message.
---
<aside class="not-prose my-6 flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm text-amber-900 dark:border-amber-700 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-100">
  <span aria-hidden="true" class="shrink-0 text-lg leading-none">🚧</span>
  <p>
    <slot><strong>Under construction.</strong> This page is still being built, so
    sections may be incomplete or change as it's fleshed out. The calculators are
    sourced and tested; treat the surrounding content as a work in progress.</slot>
  </p>
</aside>
